ca salākaggāhī ca, bhikkhutveva saṅkhaṃ gacchati. Katamehi pañcahi? Idha , bhikkhave, bhikkhu akkhamo hoti rūpānaṃ, akkhamo saddānaṃ, akkhamo gandhānaṃ, akkhamo rasānaṃ, akkhamo phoṭṭhabbānaṃ. Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu bhattādako ca hoti okāsapharaṇo ca mañcapīṭhamaddano ca salākaggāhī ca, bhikkhutveva saṅkhaṃ gacchatī’’ti. Aṭṭhamaṃ.

‘‘Kathañca, bhikkhave, rañño nāgo akkhamo hoti  rasānaṃ? Idha, bhikkhave, rañño nāgo saṅgāmagato ekissā vā tiṇodakadattiyā vimānitovihanītovihānito 
